activateStrategy().notice: Activate the current strategy set for the vault.

deposit().notice: Handles deposits from the liquidity pool

executeBound().details: Needs to be called after the update was prepraed. Fails if called before time delay is met.
executeBound().notice: Execute update of deviation bound for strategy allocation (with time delay enforced).

executeDebtLimit().details: Needs to be called after the update was prepraed. Fails if called before time delay is met.
executeDebtLimit().notice: Execute update of debt limit (with time delay enforced).

executeNewStrategy().details: Needs to be called after the update was prepraed. Fails if called before time delay is met.
executeNewStrategy().notice: Execute strategy update (with time delay enforced).

executePerformanceFee().details: Needs to be called after the update was prepraed. Fails if called before time delay is met.
executePerformanceFee().notice: Execute update of performance fee (with time delay enforced).

executeReserveFee().details: Needs to be called after the update was prepraed. Fails if called before time delay is met.
executeReserveFee().notice: Execute update of reserve fee (with time delay enforced).

executeStrategistFee().details: Needs to be called after the update was prepraed. Fails if called before time delay is met.
executeStrategistFee().notice: Execute update of strategist fee (with time delay enforced).

executeTargetAllocation().details: Needs to be called after the update was prepraed. Fails if called before time delay is met.
executeTargetAllocation().notice: Execute update of target allocation (with time delay enforced).

getBound().notice: Returns the allowed symmetric bound for target allocation (e.g. +- 5%)

getDebtLimit().notice: The debt limit that the total debt of a strategy may not exceed.

getPerformanceFee().details: The strategist is paid in LP tokens, while the remainder of the profit stays in the vault.      Default performance fee is set to 5% of harvested profits.
getPerformanceFee().notice: Returns the fee charged on a strategy's generated profits.

getReserveFee().notice: Returns the percentage of the performance fee which is allocated to the vault reserve

getStrategistFee().notice: Returns the percentage of the performance fee that goes to the strategist.

getTargetAllocation().details: this is to reduce gas costs. Withdrawals first come from idle funds and can therefore      avoid unnecessary gas costs.
getTargetAllocation().notice: The target percentage of total underlying funds to be allocated towards a strategy.

getTotalUnderlying().notice: Computes the total underlying of the vault: idle funds + allocated funds - debt

harvest().details: Harvesting adds profits to the vault's balance and deducts fees.  No performance fees are charged on profit used to repay debt.
harvest().notice: Harvest profits from the vault's strategy.

initializeStrategy(address).details: Bypasses the time delay, but can only be called if strategy is not set already.

prepareBound(uint256).notice: Prepare update of deviation bound for strategy allocation (with time delay enforced).

params.newBound: New deviation bound for target allocation.

prepareDebtLimit(uint256).notice: Prepare update of debt limit (with time delay enforced).

prepareNewStrategy(address).notice: Prepare update of the vault's strategy (with time delay enforced).

preparePerformanceFee(uint256).notice: Prepare update of performance fee (with time delay enforced).

prepareReserveFee(uint256).notice: Prepare update of reserve fee (with time delay enforced).

prepareStrategistFee(uint256).notice: Prepare update of strategist fee (with time delay enforced).

prepareTargetAllocation(uint256).notice: Prepare update of target allocation (with time delay enforced).

withdraw(uint256).details: If the specified amount exceeds idle funds, an amount of funds is withdrawn      from the strategy such that it will achieve a target allocation for after the      amount has been withdrawn.
withdraw(uint256).notice: Withdraws specified amount of underlying from vault.

withdrawAll().notice: Withdraws all funds from vault and strategy and transfer them to the pool.

withdrawAllFromStrategy().details: Harvests profits before withdrawing. Deactivates strategy after withdrawing.
withdrawAllFromStrategy().notice: Withdraws all funds from strategy to vault.

withdrawFromReserve(uint256).details: Withdraws from reserve will cause a spike in pool exchange rate.  Pool deposits should be paused during this to prevent front running
withdrawFromReserve(uint256).notice: Withdraws specified amount of underlying from reserve to vault.

withdrawFromStrategy(uint256).notice: Withdraws an amount of underlying from the strategy to the vault.
